        comparaisonTransport: "The TER Lille — Saint-Omer costs €12.60 and takes 40-50 minutes with roughly one train per hour. Saint-Omer station is a 10-minute walk from the centre but 5 km from the Audomarois marshes (no public transport to the marshes). The TaxiNeo taxi at €85 — €110 provides door-to-door service and crucially the flexibility to combine marshes + cathedral + crystal factory + Dome in one day, which is impossible by public transport. For 3-4 passengers, the cost (€22-37 per person) is competitive.",
