        comparaisonTransport: "The Lille — Roubaix metro (line 2) costs €1.80 and takes 20-25 minutes. It is frequent (every 2-5 min) and economical. However, metro stations don't cover the entire city and outlying areas require a connecting bus. The TaxiNeo taxi at €25 — €35 provides direct door-to-door service, ideal for people with luggage, families with pushchairs, visitors in a hurry or evening trips. It is also the practical choice for reaching McArthurGlen or La Piscine without walking from the metro.",
