          { question: "Does the taxi drop me on the promenade?", answer: "Yes, your driver drops you directly on the Berck-Plage seafront, at the promenade or at your accommodation." },
          { question: "Can we stop at Montreuil-sur-Mer?", answer: "Yes, Montreuil-sur-Mer is on the route. A 30-45 min stop to see the ramparts and medieval centre is possible at no significant extra cost." }
