        comparaisonTransport: "The TER from Lille to Abbeville goes via Amiens with a connection, for a total journey of 2h to 2h30 (20-35 euros). Frequency is reasonable via Amiens but connections are not always well-timed. BlaBlaCar is rare on this route. By car, expect 16 euros in fuel and 11 euros in tolls, totalling 27 euros excluding vehicle wear. The TaxiNeo taxi at 190 — 240 euros provides a direct door-to-door journey in 1h40, with no connection in Amiens. It is the preferred solution for families and tourists wishing to explore the Baie de Somme from Abbeville, as your driver can also take you directly to Saint-Valery or Le Crotoy. For 3-4 passengers, the cost of 48-80 euros per person is reasonable for direct access to one of France's most beautiful natural sites.",
